{"id":149,"parent_id":110,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":149,"title":"Alma 39","subtitle":"","short_title":"Alma","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39","content":[["div",[".intro","The commandments of Alma to his son Corianton."],[".studyIntro",["i","Comprising",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39?span=39-42"},"chapters 39 through 42"],"."]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 39"],[".studySummary",["i","Sexual sin is an abomination—Corianton’s sins kept the Zoramites from receiving the word—Christ’s redemption is retroactive in saving the faithful who preceded it. About 74",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.1","order":"05.20.039.16459"},["b","1"],"And now, my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"son"],", I have somewhat more to say unto thee than what I said unto thy brother; for behold, have ye not observed the steadiness of thy brother, his faithfulness, and his diligence in keeping the commandments of God? Behold, has he not set a good",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"example"],"for thee?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.2","order":"05.20.039.16460"},["b","2"],"For thou didst not give so much heed unto my words as did thy brother, among the people of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Zoramites"],". Now this is what I have against thee; thou didst go on unto boasting in thy strength and thy wisdom."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.3","order":"05.20.039.16461"},["b","3"],"And this is not all, my son. Thou didst do that which was grievous unto me; for thou didst forsake the ministry, and did go over into the land of Siron among the borders of the Lamanites, after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"harlot"],"Isabel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.4","order":"05.20.039.16462"},["b","4"],"Yea, she did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"steal"],"away the hearts of many; but this was no excuse for thee, my son. Thou shouldst have tended to the ministry wherewith thou wast entrusted."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.5","order":"05.20.039.16463"},["b","5"],"Know ye not, my son, that these things are an abomination in the sight of the Lord; yea, most",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"abominable"],"above all sins save it be the shedding of innocent",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"blood"],"or denying the Holy Ghost?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.6","order":"05.20.039.16464"},["b","6"],"For behold, if ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"deny"],"the Holy Ghost when it once has had place in you, and ye know that ye deny it, behold, this is a sin which is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"unpardonable"],"; yea, and whosoever murdereth against the light and knowledge of God, it is not easy for him to obtain",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"forgiveness"],"; yea, I say unto you, my son, that it is not easy for him to obtain a forgiveness."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.7","order":"05.20.039.16465"},["b","7"],"And now, my son, I would to God that ye had not been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"guilty"],"of so great a crime. I would not dwell upon your crimes, to harrow up your soul, if it were not for your good."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.8","order":"05.20.039.16466"},["b","8"],"But behold, ye cannot",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"hide"],"your crimes from God; and except ye repent they will stand as a testimony against you at the last day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.9","order":"05.20.039.16467"},["b","9"],"Now my son, I would that ye should repent and forsake your sins, and go no more after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"lusts"],"of your eyes, but",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"cross"],"yourself in all these things; for except ye do this ye can in nowise inherit the kingdom of God. Oh, remember, and take it upon you, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"cross"],"yourself in these things."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.10","order":"05.20.039.16468"},["b","10"],"And I command you to take it upon you to counsel with your elder brothers in your undertakings; for behold, thou art in thy youth, and ye stand in need to be nourished by your brothers. And give heed to their counsel."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11","order":"05.20.039.16469"},["b","11"],"Suffer not yourself to be led away by any vain or foolish thing; suffer not the devil to lead away your heart again after those wicked harlots. Behold, O my son, how great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"iniquity"],"ye brought upon the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"Zoramites"],"; for when they saw your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"conduct"],"they would not believe in my words."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.12","order":"05.20.039.16470"},["b","12"],"And now the Spirit of the Lord doth say unto me:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Command"],"thy children to do good, lest they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"lead"],"away the hearts of many people to destruction; therefore I command you, my son, in the fear of God, that ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"refrain"],"from your iniquities;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.13","order":"05.20.039.16471"},["b","13"],"That ye turn to the Lord with all your mind, might, and strength; that ye lead away the hearts of no more to do wickedly; but rather return unto them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"acknowledge"],"your faults and that wrong which ye have done."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.14","order":"05.20.039.16472"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Seek not"],"after riches nor the vain things of this world; for behold, you cannot carry them with you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.15","order":"05.20.039.16473"},["b","15"],"And now, my son, I would say somewhat unto you concerning the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"coming"],"of Christ. Behold, I say unto you, that it is he that surely shall come to take away the sins of the world; yea, he cometh to declare glad tidings of salvation unto his people."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.16","order":"05.20.039.16474"},["b","16"],"And now, my son, this was the ministry unto which ye were called, to declare these glad tidings unto this people, to prepare their minds; or rather that salvation might come unto them, that they may prepare the minds of their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"children"],"to hear the word at the time of his coming."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.17","order":"05.20.039.16475"},["b","17"],"And now I will ease your mind somewhat on this subject. Behold, you marvel why these things should be known so long beforehand. Behold, I say unto you, is not a soul at this time as precious unto God as a soul will be at the time of his coming?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.18","order":"05.20.039.16476"},["b","18"],"Is it not as necessary that the plan of redemption should be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"made"],"known unto this people as well as unto their children?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.19","order":"05.20.039.16477"},["b","19"],"Is it not as easy at this time for the Lord to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"send"],"his angel to declare these glad tidings unto us as unto our children, or as after the time of his coming?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.1a","order":"05.20.039.16478"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.7"},"Alma 31:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.1b","order":"05.20.039.16480"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/example"},"TG Example"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.2a","order":"05.20.039.16482"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/38.3"},"Alma 38:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.3a","order":"05.20.039.16484"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.22.22-25"},"1 Sam. 2:22 (22–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/5.3"},"Prov. 5:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sensuality"},"TG Sensuality"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.4a","order":"05.20.039.16486"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/7.18.6-27"},"Prov. 7:18 (6–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.5a","order":"05.20.039.16488"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adulterer"},"TG Adulterer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"Fornication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.5b","order":"05.20.039.16490"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/life-sanctity-of"},"TG Life, Sanctity of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.6a","order":"05.20.039.16492"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/8.28"},"Moro. 8:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.35"},"D&C 76:35"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Loss of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.6b","order":"05.20.039.16494"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-unpardonable-sin-against"},"TG Holy Ghost, Unpardonable Sin against"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.6c","order":"05.20.039.16496"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.18"},"Rom. 9:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.10"},"D&C 64:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.7a","order":"05.20.039.16498"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guilt"},"TG Guilt"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.8a","order":"05.20.039.16500"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.9a","order":"05.20.039.16502"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/5.8"},"Prov. 5:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/carnal-mind"},"TG Carnal Mind"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"Chastity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"Covet"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.9b","order":"05.20.039.16504"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"TG Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.9c","order":"05.20.039.16506"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.30"},"3 Ne. 12:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11a","order":"05.20.039.16508"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.24.22-25"},"1 Sam. 2:24 (22–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11b","order":"05.20.039.16510"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/35.14.2-14"},"Alma 35:14 (2–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.4.4-6,13"},"43:4 (4–6, 13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11c","order":"05.20.039.16512"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/12.14"},"2 Sam. 12:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.5"},"Ezek. 5:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/2.21.21-23"},"Rom. 2:21 (21–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.13"},"14:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.14.13-14"},"1 Cor. 9:14 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6"},"1 Ne. 21:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/4.11"},"Alma 4:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.9.8-9"},"D&C 103:9 (8–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/example"},"TG Example"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.12a","order":"05.20.039.16514"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commandments-of-god"},"TG Commandments of God"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching"},"Teaching"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.12b","order":"05.20.039.16516"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peer-influence"},"TG Peer Influence"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.12c","order":"05.20.039.16518"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abstain"},"TG Abstain"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.13a","order":"05.20.039.16520"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.35"},"Mosiah 27:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.14a","order":"05.20.039.16522"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/6.33.25-34"},"Matt. 6:33 (25–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.18.18-19"},"Jacob 2:18 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.7.6-7"},"D&C 6:7 (6–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.31.31-32"},"68:31 (31–32)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.15a","order":"05.20.039.16524"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.16a","order":"05.20.039.16526"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"},"TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.18a","order":"05.20.039.16528"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.4.4-6"},"Jacob 4:4 (4–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.19a","order":"05.20.039.16530"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.2.2-3"},"Mosiah 3:2 (2–3)"],"."]]}
